column1: What is the name of this health facility (Minene sunan wannan asibiti)
column2: A2. Patient's hospital ID (Lambar shaidar asibiti ta marar lafiya)
column3: A3i. How long have you been living with Fistula? (Tun yaushe kike zaune da yoyon fitsari?)
column4: A3ii. How did you develop the Fistula? (Yaya aka yi kika kamu da yoyon fitsari?)
column6: A4i. How old were you at last birthday? (Shikaran ki nawa?)
column7: A4ii. How old were you at your first pregnancy? (Shikaran ki nawa a lokacin cikin ki na farko?)
column8: A6i. What your state of residence ? (Menene Jihar zama)
column9: A7i.Were you married before the fistula occurred? (Kina de aure kafin yoyon fitsari ya sameki?)
column11: A8i. What is your highest level of education? (Menene matin (matsayin) illimin ki?)
column12: A9i. What is your Occupation (Menene Sana'a ki?)
column13: A9iii. Please specify your average monthly income (Saka matsakaicin kudin shigarki na wata-wata)
column14: A10i. Have you had any fistula surgery done before? (Shin an yi miki tiyatar yoyon fitsari a baya?)
column15: A10ii. If Yes, how many surgery have you had in the past? (Idan Ee, tiyata nawa aka yi muku a baya?)
column16: A11i. Who told you about the Fistula repair services? (Waya ba ki labarin aikin gyaran yoyon fitsari?)
column17: A12i. How did you get to the facility (Taya kika kawo kan ki asibiti)
column18: A13i. Who consented to this repair apart from you? (Waya yarda da wannan gyaran banda ke?)
column19: A14i. How long did you stay in the facility before the surgery was done? (Tsawon wane lokaci kika zauna a asibiti kafin a yi tiyatar?)
column20: A14ii. After the surgery, how long did you stay in the facility (hospital) before discharge? (Baya tiyata, tsawon kwanaki nawa kika zauna a asibiti kafin sallama?)
column21: A15i. Are you completely healed now? (Kin warke gaba daya?)
column22: A15ii. If no, What other challenges relating with the surgery are you still feeling? (Idan a'a, wadanne kalubale(matsala) da suka shafi aikin tiyata kike ji har yanzu?)
column23: A16i. How much did you pay for this surgery? (Nawa kika biya a wannan tiyatar?)
column24: A16ii. Were you asked to bring any item before the surgery could be performed? (An umarce ki ki kawo wani abu kafin a yi aikin tiyatar?)
column25: A16iii. If yes, what item(s) did you bring? (Idan Eh, wadanne kayayyaki aka ce ki kawo?)
column26: A17i. Do you know other woman/women who might need this care in your community? (Shin kin san wasu mata wadanda za SU iya bakatar wannan kulawa a garinku?)
column27: A19i. Is the patient physically challenged? (Shin mai haƙuri yana da ƙalubalen jiki?)
column28: B1. During medical care, I am well examined and treated. (In na je neman magani, suna mai da hankali su duba komai)
column29: B2. I have doubts about the ability of the doctors who treat me. (Ina da shakku game da kwarerar likitocin da suke kula da ni)
column30: B3. Doctors did not address my personal concerns. (Likitoci suna aiki kamar kasuwanci kuma ba su nuna min kyakkyawar alaka ba)
column31: B4. My doctor treats me in a very friendly and courteous manner. (Likitana yana kula da ni cikin sakin fuska da ladabi)
column32: B5. Doctor adequately explained the reason for medical tests done. (Likitana ya kware da kyau game da yin bayanin dalili yin gwajin Nikita)
column33: B6. I feel confident that I can get the medical care I need without being set back financially. (Ina da kwarin gwiwa cewa zan iya samun kulawar jinya da nake bukata ba tare da an mayar da ni saboda rashin kudin)
column34: B7. Doctor/healthcare provider usually spends a lot of time with me. (Likita/ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya yawanci suna ciyar da lokaci mai yawa tare da ni.)
column35: B8. I have easy access to the doctor whenever needed. (Ina samun sauƙin samun likita lokacin da nake buƙata.)
column36: * B9. I have to wait long to consult the doctor. (Dole ne in jira tsawon lokaci don tuntubar likita)
column37: * B9. I have to wait long to consult the doctor. (Dole ne in jira tsawon lokaci don tuntubar likita)/FALSE
column38: * B10. How do you feel now that you’re getting discharged? (Yaya kuke ji yanzu da za a sallame ku?)
column39: B11. I will recommend this facility to my family or friends. (Zan ba da shawarar wannan asibitin ga 'Yan uwana da abokaina)
column40: B12. Health facility Environment cleanliness (Tsaftar muhallin wurin lafiya)
